WE ARE

DISRUPTIVE
TRANSPARENT
RELENTLESS


xAd provides real-time, location-based marketing, without the guesswork.
Since 2009, xAd has grown from four founders to hundreds of employees
across three continents that serve millions of consumers and marketers.
Find out more about our journey and what drives our team.


