xAd, Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg










































  





















































































July 21, 2017 9:39 PM ET
Internet Software and Services

Company Overview of xAd, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
xAd, Inc. provides a location-based marketing and advertising platform for publishers and developers. The company offers in-store targeting, proximity targeting, audience targeting, audience search, and measurement solutions; provides a self-serve marketing platform for real-time location-based campaign planning, buying, and reporting; allows users to find the right audiences based on the places they visit; provides actionable insights; and delivers access to large scale location-verified mobile audiences. It also allows users to amplify their media buys with location; enables users to create their own new campaign or make adjustments to a current campaign in real-time; provides a marketing ...
xAd, Inc. provides a location-based marketing and advertising platform for publishers and developers. The company offers in-store targeting, proximity targeting, audience targeting, audience search, and measurement solutions; provides a self-serve marketing platform for real-time location-based campaign planning, buying, and reporting; allows users to find the right audiences based on the places they visit; provides actionable insights; and delivers access to large scale location-verified mobile audiences. It also allows users to amplify their media buys with location; enables users to create their own new campaign or make adjustments to a current campaign in real-time; provides a marketing platform that offers access to competitive and behavioral trends, and the ability to create, execute, and measure campaigns; and offers location-targeted mobile advertising. xAd, Inc. was formerly known as V-ENABLE, Inc. The company was founded in 2001 and is based in New York, New York.
Detailed Description


One World Trade60th FloorNew York, NY 10007United StatesFounded in 2001



Phone: 888-234-7893

www.xad.com







