Company Profile
Sector: Communications
Industry: Media
Sub-Industry: Advertising & Marketing
xAD, Inc. provides mobile marketing solutions. The Company offers mobile-local adverting network, and also aggregates and manages location-specific advertising requests for national and local advertisers. xAD serves enterprises throughout the United States.




