This is a brand page for the XAD BLUEPRINTS trademark by xAD, Inc. 
                                in New York, NY, 10007.
Write a review about a product or service associated with this XAD BLUEPRINTS trademark.    
                                Or, contact the owner xAD, Inc. of the XAD BLUEPRINTS trademark by filing a request to communicate with    
                                the Legal Correspondent for licensing, use, and/or questions related to the XAD BLUEPRINTS trademark.
                           






On Wednesday, May 27, 2015,  a U.S. federal trademark registration was filed for 
                        XAD BLUEPRINTS by 
                        xAD, Inc., New York, NY  10007.
                        The USPTO has given the XAD BLUEPRINTS 
                        trademark serial  number of  86642332.  
                        The current federal status of this trademark filing is REGISTERED.
                        The correspondent listed for XAD BLUEPRINTS is 
                        
                        
                                            THOMAS M. HADID of 
                                            COOLEY LLP,  1299 Pennsylvania Ave NW Ste 700, Washington, DC 20004-2446 
                                .
                            The XAD BLUEPRINTS trademark is filed in the category of 
                            
                                    Computer & Software Services & Scientific Services
                                . 
                            The description provided to the USPTO for XAD BLUEPRINTS 
                            is Software as a service for the storage and protection of private information, media, and data. 
                            





